RESOLUTION

HP has made the following patch kits available to resolve the vulnerability.

Patch kit Name
 Location

HP SSL 1.4-467 (Based on OpenSSL 0.9.8w)
 http://h71000.www7.hp.com/openvms/products/ssl/ssl.html

